maine gandhi ko ( hindi : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2001 indian hindi film directed by om prakash rao . the film features an ensemble cast consisting of aamir khan , naseeruddin shah , and boman irani in the lead roles . the film had its world premiere at the indian panorama section of the 2015 cannes film festival .